15 WHEREAS, known for his innovative coaching methods, including his emphasis on frequent
16 throwing between starts, Leo Mazzone revolutionized the way pitchers prepared for
17 competition and left a lasting impact on the game; and
18 WHEREAS, his dedication, expertise, and ability to maximize the potential of his pitchers
19 earned him widespread respect throughout the baseball community, culminating in his
20 induction into the Braves Hall of Fame in 2022; and
21 WHEREAS, the induction of Leo Mazzone into the Georgia Sports Hall of Fame is a fitting
22 tribute to his legacy as a visionary coach and a key architect of one of baseball's greatest
23 dynasties.
24 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
25 the members of this body congratulate Leo Mazzone upon his induction into the Georgia
26 Sports Hall of Fame and extend the most sincere best wishes for future health and happiness.
27 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
28 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Leo
29 Mazzone.
